headline: Why Are MGM Resorts (MGM) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of hospitality and casino entertainment company MGM Resorts (NYSE:MGM) jumped 6.1% in the afternoon session after the recent Las Vegas F1 weekend provided a significant boost to the company, attracting a large number of visitors and setting new betting records.
